Resource Profile: PT_RelatedPerson

Official URL: http://hl7.pt/fhir/core/StructureDefinition/52d49cef-b06f-4aa7-859d-26a002df32c1 Version: 0.0.1
Active as of 2024-09-23 Computable Name: PT_RelatedPerson

A generic RelatedPerson resource for Portugal

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: Operation, PT_Condition, PT_Coverage, PT_Encounter... Show 4 more, PT_MedicationAdministration, PT_NutritionOrder, PT_Procedure and Reporter
